==English==
===Etymology===
From Japanese [[切腹]] (せっぷく, seppuku).

===Noun===
'''seppuku''' (''uncountable'')

#a form of [[ritual]] [[suicide]] by [[disembowelment]], practiced by Japanese [[samurai]], especially to rid oneself of shame.

====Synonyms====
*[[hara-kiri]]

====Derived terms====
*[[commit seppuku]]

